styles.desc: The art style is 3D rendering with cartoonish features and plain white backgrounds.
styles.more_info: Smooth, glossy textures, exaggerated proportions, vibrant colors, realistic lighting effects, and a blend of cartoonish and semi-realistic details.

styles.desc: Black and white cartoon line art with plain backgrounds.
styles.more_info: Thick, clean black lines, minimal details, and a monochromatic black-and-white color scheme, emphasizing simplicity and clarity.

styles.desc: The art style is realistic monochrome photography with plain backgrounds and detailed textures.
styles.more_info: High contrast, rich tonal gradients, fine texture details, dramatic lighting, and an emphasis on emotion and timeless aesthetics.

styles.desc: Intricate black and white crosshatching drawings, showcasing realistic detail and texture.
styles.more_info: Intricate linework, overlapping strokes, fine texture details, high contrast, and a hand-drawn, engraving-like aesthetic.

styles.desc: Dynamic sports poster style with vibrant colors, bold typography, and a cinematic composition.
styles.more_info: Vivid colors, energetic compositions, dramatic lighting, action-packed scenes, bold typography, and a focus on movement and excitement.

styles.desc: The art style is cartoon with soft watercolor textures and minimalistic features, often showcasing plain or simple backgrounds.
styles.more_info: Playful linework, vibrant watercolor-like fills, soft textures, organic shapes, and a whimsical, hand-drawn aesthetic.

styles.desc: The style is realistic with neutral backgrounds to emphasize the textures and details.
styles.more_info: Professional composition, soft lighting, clean backgrounds, natural yet polished appearances, and a formal, approachable aesthetic.

styles.desc: Silhouette photography with dramatic lighting and strong contrast.
styles.more_info: Dark, featureless shapes against a bright background, strong contrast, minimal detail, and a focus on form and outline to convey emotion and composition.

styles.desc: Vintage photography style, sepia tones, and classic poses with a historical aesthetic.
styles.more_info: Sepia or muted tones, soft focus, grainy textures, retro compositions, and a nostalgic, timeless aesthetic.

styles.desc: Cinematic, dark and moody, with stylized lighting and distinct color grading.
styles.more_info: High contrast, and an atmospheric, dramatic tone that evokes tension or mystery.
